  <description>
    <p>
      Akkhara is a multilingual dictionary designed to enhance the way you explore and understand languages. Akkhara aims not just to simply be a dictionary; it&apos;s your linguistic companion, offering a seamless and enriching experience for language enthusiasts, students, professionals and casual users alike.
    </p>
    <p>
      Some of the most highlighting features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Comprehensive word database</li>
      <li>Multilingual support</li>
      <li>Keyword search and in-definition word search</li>
      <li>Approximative keyword search (fuzzy search)</li>
      <li>Multi-dictionary search</li>
      <li>Offline access</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

